S&P Downgrades Hipotecaria Su Casita Notes to ’D’ After Missed Payment

-- B y   L a u r a   Z e l e n k o
-- 
2011-04-05T19:25:18Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-05/s-p-downgrades-hipotecaria-su-casita-notes-to-d-after-missed-payment.html
Hipotecaria Su Casita SA’s long-term
credit rating was cut to D from CC by  Standard & Poor’s  after
the Mexican company missed an interest payment on $150 million
of senior unsecured notes.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Laura Zelenko at 
 lzelenko@bloomberg.net  